http://www.sprezzatech.com/sprezzos.html

This repository builds and tests SprezzOS install media.

Dependencies
------------

Updating requires Subversion, git, and mr (consult debian-installer/README).

Building requires GNU make, subversion-tools (svn-clean), and simple-cdd.

Building SPL/ZFS requires uuid-dev, libz-dev, autoconf and alien. Note that
 ZFS requires a *non*-preemptive kernel (CONFIG_PREEMPT=n).

Building debian-installer requires a number of packages; perform an

	apt-get build-dep debian-installer

and run dpkg_checkbuilddeps until it shows nothing missing.

Testing adds a dependency on KVM.
